title: Whalecam reveals secrets of Antarctic minke
text:
Whalecam reveals secrets of Antarctic minke 5:51am EST - 01:59 
Secrets of the minke whale have been revealed, thanks to scientists from University of California Santa-Cruz. They fitted whales off the Antartarctic Peninsula with cameras funded by WWF-Australia.
